# IF-01 Wave-3 Scaffolds — Fork/Exec/Wait/Pipe/Dup2
# ============================================================================
# All five dispatch to scheduler::clone_task / exec_into / wait_for in wave-4.
# Wave-3 returns ENOSYS (-38) so userspace linking resolves and callers
# can fail loudly instead of deadlocking.

@export("C", name: "spl_handle_fork")
